  • Classes in ohha.puzzlecrafter.grid used by ohha.puzzlecrafter.auxiliary 
    Class and Description
    CellCoordinate
    Represents coordinates of a cell in the puzzle grid.
    Grid
    This class serves as a conceptual wrapper for a two-dimensional integer array containing the puzzle grid cells' values.
    Partition
    Represents a partition of the puzzle grid, such as the nine 3x3 boxes of a regular Sudoku.
  • Classes in ohha.puzzlecrafter.grid used by ohha.puzzlecrafter.grid 
    Class and Description
    CellCoordinate

    EdgeCoordinate
    Represents coordinates of an edge in the grid.
    Grid
    This class serves as a conceptual wrapper for a two-dimensional integer array containing the puzzle grid cells' values.
    Partition
    Represents a partition of the puzzle grid, such as the nine 3x3 boxes of a regular Sudoku.
    Region
    Represents a set of cells forming a region, for example the 3x3 boxes in Sudoku or the regions in Star Battle.
    Side
    Used to refer to the edges of the grid as sides of cells.
